comment: Correctly called out of bounds.
Aldridge (SAS) and Dieng (MIN) grab and pull one another during rebounding.
Wiggins (MIN) and Green (SAS) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Mills (SAS) makes body to body contact with Wiggins (MIN) that affects the shot attempt.
Dieng (MIN) grabs Aldridge's (SAS) jersey and affects his FOM off ball.
Leonard (SAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Towns (MIN).
Gasol (SAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Wiggins (MIN) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Gasol (SAS) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically on the driving shot attempt by Towns (MIN).
Wiggins (MIN) legally contests Leonard's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Wiggins (MIN) and Leonard (SAS) briefly engage and separate off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Rubio (MIN) moves his pivot foot.
Aldridge (SAS) makes marginal contact with Towns (MIN) that does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
Green (SAS) makes marginal contact with Rubio (MIN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Towns (MIN) makes contact with Aldridge (SAS) that affects his ability to control the rebound.
Bjelica (MIN) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Aldridge (SAS) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact with Gasol (SAS) after Rubio (MIN) retrieves the rebound.
Bjelica (MIN) extends his arm into Mills (SAS) and affects his ability to defend the play.
[Detectable with stop watch] Aldridge (SAS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Aldridge (SAS) and Bjelica (MIN) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Rush (MIN) legally contests the shot attempt by Green (SAS).
Rubio (MIN) commits a take foul on Green (SAS).
Mills (SAS) commits a take foul on Wiggins (MIN).
